  • Importing Example Code into Eclipse

    1. From the Eclipse menu bar, select File > Import...
    2. Select General > Existing Projects into Workspace, and click Next
    3. Select the Select archive file: radio button
    4. Click the Browse...; button
    5. Navigate to [Platform]/[build version]/demos/eclipse within your Link-OS Multiplatform SDK installation directory (where [Platform] is the desired platform and [build version] corresponds to the desired build)
    6. Select the DeveloperDemo_Desktop.zip file
    7. Click the Finish button
